stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> BuyerLoggedIn: User logs in as Buyer

    BuyerLoggedIn --> ClickBecomeSeller: Clicks "Become a Seller"
    ClickBecomeSeller --> FillApplicationForm: Application form displayed

    FillApplicationForm --> ValidateInput: Submits form
    ValidateInput --> ShowError: Validation fails
    ShowError --> FillApplicationForm: User corrects input

    ValidateInput --> SubmitApplication: Validation passes
    SubmitApplication --> PendingStatus: Status = "pending"

    PendingStatus --> AdminReviews: Admin opens Seller Requests

    state AdminDecision <<choice>>
    AdminReviews --> AdminDecision: Admin reviews application

    AdminDecision --> Approved: Approve
    AdminDecision --> Rejected: Reject (with reason)

    Approved --> RoleUpdated: User role changed to "seller"
    RoleUpdated --> SellerFeatures: Seller sees Add Property, Dashboard, Analytics

    Rejected --> ShowRejection: User sees rejection reason
    ShowRejection --> FillApplicationForm: User can reapply

    SellerFeatures --> [*]
